title: 209 - The Turn of the Space Parasite
description: Today’s episode of The POD kicks off with a FULL BARN! The boys all catch up on their weekend and then jump right into the Pod FOD. The Pod FOD is a folder compiled of all things from the internet. Todays FOD includes The Northman’s sweet reviews, a look at the new John Wayne Gacy Doc. Stranger things new season trailer, and much much more. Make sure to subscribe to youtube.come/thepodpmi to watch full episodes and don't forget to send your submissions for the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you rocking with us and we'll see you Wednesday, Cheers.
